
[1]delicious

   DELICIOUS, a.

   1. Highly pleasing to the taste; most sweet or grateful to the senses;
   affording exquisite pleasure; as a delicious viand; delicious fruit or
   wine.

   2. Most pleasing to the mind; very grateful; yielding exquisite
   delight; as, this poem affords a delicious entertainment.
